# 📚 Teacher Toolkit - Sensei Toolkit

**Professional educational resources designed to enhance teaching and learning experiences.**

🌐 Live site: [senseitoolkit.com](https://senseitoolkit.com/)

---

## About

Teacher Toolkit is a collection of free, browser-based tools and resources for educators. The site is hosted on GitHub Pages and built with static HTML/CSS/JS — no frameworks or build tools required. Teachers can use these tools to set up learning centers, access guides, and run interactive activities directly in the browser.

